  "body": "<center>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/844397409698185227/1154994500456960010/ec_create_plugin_title.png\" alt=\"EC Mod Plugin for Cataclysm\" width=\"600\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ec-create-compat\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_64h.png\" alt=\"CurseForge\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3.1.2/assets/cozy/requires/cloth-config-api_64h.png\" alt=\"Requires Cloth Config API\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/curios\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/844397409698185227/1152401406247047188/curios_api_64h.png\" alt=\"Requires Cloth Config API\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/expanded-combat\" >\n         <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/844397409698185227/1152636014880366763/expanded_combat_64h.png\" alt=\"Requires Expanded Combat\" width=\"288\"/>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/create\" >\n         <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/844397409698185227/1154998175355113482/create_64h.png\" alt=\"Requires Create\" >\n    </a>\n</p>\n</center>\n\n\n\nA plugin Mod for [Expanded Combat](https://modrinth.com/mod/expanded-combat) adding compatibility with [Create](https://modrinth.com/mod/create).\n\n### adds support for:\nBrass - shields, arrows, bows, crossbows, weapons, quivers, and gauntlets\nMecanical Brass - Broad Sword, Claymore, Glaive, Katana, Scythe\n\n> Mechanical brass has the special ability to gain heat from blaze burners and then for a limited number of hits deal that heat out on mobs you attack.\n\n\\\n\\\nClick the banner to get the discount:\n<a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/userofbricks\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n        <img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/c94a16d8-7267-4fc5-bf4a-b064ecdd546a.webp\" alt=\"Bisect Hosting Promotional\">\n    </a>",
